trans-unit.source: Specifies the formats used with text-related methods of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Clipboard"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataObject"></xref> classes.
This enumeration contains values that are similar to the text-related fields of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataFormats> type.

This enumeration is used with the following methods: - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Clipboard.ContainsText%28System.Windows.Forms.TextDataFormat%29?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Clipboard.GetText%28System.Windows.Forms.TextDataFormat%29?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Clipboard.SetText%28System.String%2CSystem.Windows.Forms.TextDataFormat%29?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataObject.ContainsText%28System.Windows.Forms.TextDataFormat%29?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataObject.GetText%28System.Windows.Forms.TextDataFormat%29?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataObject.SetText%28System.String%2CSystem.Windows.Forms.TextDataFormat%29?displayProperty=fullName>
Specifies a comma-separated value (CSV) format, which is a common interchange format used by spreadsheets.
Specifies text consisting of HTML data.
Specifies text consisting of rich text format (RTF) data.
Specifies the standard ANSI text format.
Specifies the standard Windows Unicode text format.
